c: 13
v: 30
t: "Thus have we sent thee amongst a People before whom (long since) have (other) Peoples (gone and) passed away; in order that thou mightest rehearse unto them what We send down unto thee by inspiration; yet do they reject (Him), the Most Gracious! Say: \"He is my Lord! There is no god but He! On Him is my trust, and to Him do I turn"